H0.text: What is the capital of Australia's Northern Territory. Alice Springs

H1.text: What is the capital of Australia's Northern Territory. Katherine

H2.text: What is the capital of Australia's Northern Territory. Tennant Creek

H3.text: What is the capital of Australia's Northern Territory. Darwin

A4.text: Darwin is the capital and largest city of the Northern Territory, Australia.

A5.text: The Legislative Assembly of the Northern Territory convenes in Darwin in the Northern Territory Parliament House.
